    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a car that requires absolutely no work and looks brand new.",
