    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in impeccable condition. This vehicle reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market, maintaining its factory-fresh aesthetic and mechanical integrity. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paint, has been preserved to meet the expectations of the most discerning collector. Rigorously inspected and turn-key ready, this offering represents a premier investment in automotive excellence.",
      "price": 44900.0,
